videos.headline: Texas A&M first big play puts them in Alabama territory
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond hits Trayveon Williams for a 31-yard pass and moves them to the Alabama 39-yard line.

videos.headline: Harris' 75-yard scamper puts Alabama in front
videos.description: Alabama RB Damien Harris breaks free for a 75-yard run and puts Alabama in front 7-3.

videos.headline: Texas A&M fumble sets up Alabama at midfield
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond fumbles on a hit by Shaun Dion Hamilton, and the ball is recoverd by Rashaan Evans at the 50-yard line.

videos.headline: Hurts' run moves Alabama into Texas A&M territory
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts evades defenders and runs for 38 yards to the Texas A&M 37-yard line.

videos.headline: Texas A&M fumble gives Alabama ball in Aggie territory
videos.description: Trayveon Williams fumbles on his one-yard run and the ball is recovered by Alab Raekwon Davis at the Texas A&M 43-yard line.

videos.headline: Harris' second big run of night has Alabama on doorstep
videos.description: Alabama RB Damien Harris 27-yard dash moves offense to the Texas A&M one-yard line.

videos.headline: Hurts 1-yard TD run gives Alabama 14 point edge
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts runs right and finds the end zone for the one-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Saban: 'Too much pressure in the pocket'
videos.description: Alabama head coach Nick Saban explains what he thought of their run game and how the linebackers have played in the first half against Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Sumlin: 'Comes down to big plays and turnovers'
videos.description: Texas A&M head coach Kevin Sumlin breaks down what has gone wrong for his defense and what he said to his team in the locker room at halftime.

videos.headline: Hurts connects with Ridley for 30-yard pass
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts hooks up with Calvin Ridley for a 30-yard pass and moves the offense to the Texas A&M 24-yard line.

videos.headline: Hurts' second TD toss pads Alabama lead
videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts hits Henry Ruggs III for an eight-yard touchdown pass and gives them a 24-3 lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Alabama fumble stalls drive near midfield
videos.description: Alabama WR Robert Foster has the ball knocked loose by Debione Renfro and is recovered by Deshawn Capers-Smith.

videos.headline: Ratley's long gain gets Texas A&M in business
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond hits Damion Ratley for 32-yard pass and moves them to the Alabama three-yard line.

videos.headline: Mond evades rush, hits Kirk for great TD catch
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond dodges rushers and hits Christian Kirk for a tough two-yard touchdown to cut the Alabama lead to 24-10.

videos.headline: Texas A&M drive ends with pick at one-yard line
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond is intercepted by Minkah Fitzpatrick at the Alabam one-yard line.

videos.headline: Texas A&M blocks Alabama's punt for safety
videos.description: Texas A&M blocks Alabama punter JK Scott's punt which goes out the back of the end zone for a safety to cut the lead to 24-12.

videos.headline: Mond one-yard TD run cuts into Alabama lead late
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond runs in for a one-yard touchdown run cutting the Alabama lead to 27-19.

videos.headline: Blackledge: 'Hurts did a great job keeping offensive team calm'
videos.description: Joe Tessitore and Todd Blackledge break down the Jalen Hurts' play and how Alabama stayed undefeated.

videos.headline: Alabama holds on to beat Texas A&M
videos.description: The No. 1 Crimson Tide hold a 24-3 lead in the third quarter but need to recover a late onside kick to beat the Aggies 27-19.
